ion of new satellites onto\nhosts once they reach 0.6-0.8 R$_{200}$ radii from the cluster.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Oct 2019 18:08:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-16"}
