e parton scattering of pions is\nexactly equal to the geometric cross section, $\\sigma_{\\rm eff}=\\pi \\langle\n\\vec{b}^2 \\rangle$ and yields about 20~mb.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 8 Oct 2019 22:26:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 7 Jan 2020 11:22:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-29"}
