over, we show that BECs still well--fit the galaxy rotation\ncurves and, more importantly, could lead to an understanding of the dark matter\nnature from first principles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Oct 2019 04:52:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 May 2020 00:02:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-27"}
