d up to which ratio an\nequilibrium between ion-generation and ion-clearing is established. Hereby,\nseveral ion species and configurations of electrodes are considered in\ncombination with typical beam parameters of high-brightness electron\naccelerators. Furthermore, we present detailed numerical studies of the\nperformance of multi-purpose clearing electrodes planned for bERLinPro.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 9 Oct 2019 14:35:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-10"}
